         </tr>
         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="1">$a - Organization (R) <br>$b - Arrangement (R) <br>$c - Hierarchical level (NR) <br></td>
            <td colspan="1">$3 - Materials specified (NR) <br>$6 - Linkage (NR) <br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R) <br></td>
