      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$b - Arrangement</strong> <div class="description">Pattern of arrangement of materials within a unit (e.g., alphabetical,
                              chronological, by country, by office of origin, etc.).
         </div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">For <strong>computer files</strong>, subfield &#8225;b contains information
                                 about the sort sequence.
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
               <tr>
                  <td valign="top" width="5%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
                  <td valign="top" width="10%" align="left"></td>
