                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>##</strong><strong>$c</strong>Series;<strong>$b</strong>Alphabetical by sitter.
                  </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>351</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>##</strong><strong>$c</strong>Series;<strong>$a</strong>Organized into five subseries;<strong>$b</strong>Arranged by form of material.
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$3 - Materials specified</strong> <div class="description">Part of the described materials to which the field applies.</div>
